title: Suggestion During Drive
text:

Also the worse part of that is, it will minimize your map and asks you to accept or decline the the option, I find this is very dangerous especially when you are driving on highway with the speed of up to 60m/hr.
I hope google stop doing for the safety of drivers and their passengers.

title: I used google maps every day for work
text:
Hi Devs and Developers

I hope my message reaches you. Yall have always accepted and added my requested features. 

Iâ€™ve discovered another major inconvenience. When looking up and navigating to some stores or restaurants while trying to â€œadd a stopâ€ the location sometimes is INSIDE of a mall, college or private campus. There needs to be a flag or notification that this isnâ€™t easily accessible or perhaps no drive through for fast food. 

Written:2018?
Hello, Iâ€™ve used your app everyday of my life for 9 years. Amazing and itâ€™s made my life better. I drive to three different addresses a day to visit random customers all around my state. I use it to navigate to gas and food along the way. Some feedback I would like to request is to provide estimated cost for tolls on suggested routes. Iâ€™ve found that Iâ€™m out on toll roads for one exit making it almost pointless to enter a toll road. Or some option to only use toll roads if it saves me more than 10-20 minutes. There are also plenty of mislabeled exits. There should be a way to notify the app if there is a major issue that I run into daily where the gps puts me on the opposite side of the highway.
